==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exagitate
<hw>Ex*ag"i*tate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>exagitatus</ets>, p. p. of <ets>exagitare</ets>. See <er>Ex-</er>,
and <er>Agitate</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To stir up; to
agitate.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Arbuthnot.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To satirize; to censure severely.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Hooker.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exagitation</ent>⟦br⟧
